title: EPN-110
extract_protocol_ch1: RNeasy (Qiagen) extraction of total RNA was performed according to the manufacturer's instructions.
label_protocol_ch1: Biotinylated cRNA were prepared according to the standard Affymetrix protocol (Expression Analysis Technical Manual, 2001, Affymetrix).
hyb_protocol: Following fragmentation, 11.5 ug of cRNA were hybridized for 16 hr at 45C on GeneChips. GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix Fluidics Station 450
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the Affymetrix Gene Chip Scanner 7G.
description: Gene expression data from surgical tumor sample of ependymoma,[collection protocol] Tumor samples were snap frozen in liquid nitrogen or transferred to RNAlater immediately after surgical removal as part of patient care. All samples were collected with appropriate IRB approval (COM-IRB#95-500 and 09-0906 )
data_processing: Microarray .CEL file data was background corrected and normalized using the gcRMA algorithm, resulting in log 2 expression values. The Affymetrix HG-U133 plus 2 microarray contains 54,675 probe sets including multiple probe sets for the same gene. In order to reduce error associated with multiple testing we used only a single probe set for each gene that possessed the highest gcRMA expression level across all our samples. This filtered list of the best expressed probe sets contained 21,050 genes.

hyb_protocol: Following fragmentation, 11.5 ug of cRNA were hybridized for 16 hr at 45C on GeneChips. GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix Fluidics Station 450
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the Affymetrix Gene Chip Scanner 7G.
description: Gene expression data from surgical tumor sample of glioblastoma,[collection protocol] Tumor samples were snap frozen in liquid nitrogen or transferred to RNAlater immediately after surgical removal as part of patient care. All samples were collected with appropriate IRB approval (COM-IRB#95-500 and 09-0906 )
data_processing: Microarray .CEL file data was background corrected and normalized using the gcRMA algorithm, resulting in log 2 expression values. The Affymetrix HG-U133 plus 2 microarray contains 54,675 probe sets including multiple probe sets for the same gene. In order to reduce error associated with multiple testing we used only a single probe set for each gene that possessed the highest gcRMA expression level across all our samples. This filtered list of the best expressed probe sets contained 21,050 genes.
